== 比较 ==
AMP常被与[[Facebook_Instant_Articles|Facebook Instant Articles]]和[[苹果新闻|苹果新闻]]比较<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://venturebeat.com/2016/08/14/google-amp-vs-facebook-instant-articles/|title=Why I prefer Google AMP pages to Facebook Instant Articles|last=Novet|first=Jordan|date=August 14, 2016|website=VentureBeat|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103519/http://venturebeat.com/2016/08/14/google-amp-vs-facebook-instant-articles/|archive-date=2020-11-08|access-date=February 28, 2019|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.viget.com/articles/your-guide-to-mobile-publishing-formats-amp-facebook-instant-articles-and-apple-news/|title=Your Guide to Mobile Publishing Formats: AMP, Facebook Instant Articles, and Apple News {{pipe}} Viget|last=Travis|first=Ben|last2=|first2=|date=December 13, 2016|website=viget.com|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108151119/https://www.viget.com/articles/your-guide-to-mobile-publishing-formats-amp-facebook-instant-articles-and-apple-news/|archive-date=2020-11-08|access-date=February 28, 2019|last3=|first3=|last4=|first4=|last5=|first5=|last6=|dead-url=no}}</ref>，三者都发布于2015年，旨在提供更快的移动内容。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2015/06/08Apple-Announces-News-App-for-iPhone-iPad/|title=Apple Announces News App for iPhone & iPad|work=Apple Newsroom|access-date=August 31, 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024183502/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2015/06/08Apple-Announces-News-App-for-iPhone-iPad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>AMP项目的支持者声称：APM是发布者和技术公司间的合作成果；AMP是为互联网，而不是专属应用程序设计的。

== 应用 ==
部分媒体已开始使用AMP，包括[[CNN|CNN]]、[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]和[[福克斯新闻|福克斯新闻]]。安装第三方插件后，[[WordPress|WordPress]]博客也可使用AMP<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wpmyweb.com/seo/setup-google-amp-wordpress-plugin.html |title=How to Setup Google AMP on WordPress Site (Using AMP Plugin) |website=Wpmyweb.com |date=2017-02-07 |author=Jyoti Prakash Ray |accessdate=2017-03-07 |language=en |archive-date=2017-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210232009/http://www.wpmyweb.com/seo/setup-google-amp-wordpress-plugin.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年3月7日，Google宣布[[百度|百度]]、[[搜狗|搜狗]]和[[Yahoo!_JAPAN|Yahoo! JAPAN]]搜索将支持AMP<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ampproject.org/latest/blog/amp-grows-its-footprint/ |title=AMP grows its footprint – Accelerated Mobile Pages Project |accessdate=2017-03-08 |work=www.ampproject.org |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308152856/https://www.ampproject.org/latest/blog/amp-grows-its-footprint/ |archivedate=2017-03-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；其中百度在搜索结果中将AMP页面标注为“MIP”（移动网页加速器），一个百度主导、与AMP类似的项目<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mipengine.org/ |title=MIP官网_移动网页加速器_MIP(Mobile Instant Pages) |accessdate=2017-03-08 |work=www.mipengine.org |language=zh-cn |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219094850/https://www.mipengine.org/ |archivedate=2017-02-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

